title: One Bed in Great Location! In-unit Washer/Dryer & Dishwasher! Pets OK!
posting_body: ['This beautiful Redwood City apartment on the first floor will be move in ready by August 20th.', 'Safe community and pet friendly!', 'Includes:', '- Great kitchen with stainless steel appliances (refrigerator, gas stove, dishwasher and microwave), wood cabinets, and granite counter tops', '- Recessed lighting in living area', '- Hardwood floors in living area, kitchen, and hallway', '- New carpet in bedroom', '- Dual bedroom closets', '- Washer & Dryer in unit', '- Great floor plan with lots of natural light', '- Double-pane glass windows with good sound insulation', '- New interior/exterior paint', '- Cable ready', '- One assigned carport with additional storage cabinets', '- Easy street parking', '- New landscaping', '- Landlord pays water, sewage, and trash', 'Virtual Tour: <URL>', 'Great Location:', '- 5 min.', 'walk to Safeway, Walgreens, Whole Foods, Starbucks, etc.', '- 10 min.', 'walk to Wellesley Park, trails, and vibrant downtown area along El Camino and Broadway St.', '- 4 min.', 'drive to Whole Foods, Rite Aid, CVS, and restaurants on Los Gatos Blvd.', '- 25 min.', 'commute to major employers including Stanford, Facebook, and Google -', 'Top ranking schools', '- Easy freeway access', 'Requirements:', '- One year lease required', '- Non-smoking property', '- Pet Restrictions: Cats are okay.', 'Dogs under 50 lbs are okay.', 'Qualification Criteria:', '- Minimum Income Amount: 2.5x monthly rent from verifiable sources', '- Credit:', 'Good credit with no evictions or bankruptcy', '- Rental History:', 'Good recommendation from current landlord', 'Rent: $2745', 'Deposit: $1,500', 'Pet Rent: $60 per pet', 'Pet Deposit: $500', 'We look forward to meeting you!', 'Happy apartment hunting!', 'Owner pays for water, sewage, and trash.', 'Tenant is responsible for gas and electricity.', 'Managed by Orvick Management Group INC BRE#: 01915642']
